#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:20
msgid ""
"The ``PkgConfigDeps`` is the dependencies generator for pkg-config. "
"Generates pkg-config files named *<PKG-NAME>.pc* (where ``<PKG-NAME`` is the "
"name declared by dependencies in ``cpp_info.names[\"pkg_config\"]`` if "
"specified), containing a valid pkg-config file syntax. Indeed, it can also "
"be defined using ``set_property`` and the property ``pkg_config_name`` "
"(available since Conan 1.36), for instance:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:25
msgid ""
"self.cpp_info.components[\"mycomponent\"].set_property(\"pkg_config_name\", "
"\"mypkg-config-name\")"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools/gnu/pkgconfigdeps.rst:31
msgid ""
"In Conan 2.0 that will be the default way of setting those properties and "
"also passing custom properties to generators. Check the :ref:`cpp_info "
"attributes reference <cpp_info_attributes_reference>` for more information."
msgstr ""

